{"tid":2145594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"貝魯特巨爆重燃反政府示威  警催淚彈驅散 當局拘16人圖息民怨","createTime":"2020-08-08T06:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T06:43:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"803c0edd0906b329f222d34bf5f2e39707dfaa66","tid":2145594,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200808/TVYAB7KYFNFTS2LDKYMKUFWLGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200808%2FTVYAB7KYFNFTS2LDKYMKUFWLGY%2F&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=bc6b83f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200808%2FTVYAB7KYFNFTS2LDKYMKUFWLGY%2F&h=04c1c51b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200808/TVYAB7KYFNFTS2LDKYMKUFWLGY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n貝魯特巨爆重燃反政府示威 <br />\n警催淚彈驅散 當局拘16人圖息民怨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/P3g-_nc5jvnucH2NDPsVrGjOtxc=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RE67SP7RH3GU7YX5Z6RD4PS3D4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FP3g-_nc5jvnucH2NDPsVrGjOtxc%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRE67SP7RH3GU7YX5Z6RD4PS3D4.jpg&h=a41068ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貝魯特港口滿目瘡痍，重建勢必困難重重。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩首都貝魯特港口周初發生大爆炸，造成逾150人死亡，重燃因武漢肺炎稍歇的民怨，數十名示威者前日到國會附近抗議政府無能，遭警方以催淚彈驅散；當局為息眾怒積極問責，拘留16名港口人員。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：船東因貪改道被扣種禍根<br />\n<br />\n官方媒體前日報道，軍警在貝魯特中部與數十名反政府示威者衝突，示威者聚在國會附近放火，又向警員擲石，警員以催淚彈驅散人群，部份示威者受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n600萬人陷糧食危機<br />\n<br />\n為息眾怒，政府成立委員會調查爆炸案，要求四天內查出爆炸原因，初步認為有火源引爆存放在港口倉庫的2,750噸硝酸銨；。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中央銀行已下令凍結七名港口和海關官員財產，以及發出旅遊禁令，對象包括關長達希爾及出事港口總經理庫雷特姆。<br />\n<br />\n是次爆炸亦引發糧食短缺危機，以麵包為主糧、人口600萬的黎巴嫩十分倚賴進口食物，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，現只能依靠各個零散私營磨坊存在小型倉庫備用的小麥。<br />\n<br />\n面對上世紀內戰以來最差的經濟，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。：我們不能再姑息他們，統統非走不可。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩官員辭職促改革<br />\n<br />\n一方有難，各國紛紛施以援手，美國已派出C-17軍用運輸機載同首批11大櫃糧食、水和醫療物資送到黎巴嫩；。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，為緩解床位荒，約旦、卡塔爾、俄羅斯和伊朗等國亦資助黎巴嫩搭建六間臨時醫院，前日起火速啟用。據當地媒體報道，俄羅斯援助的醫院可容100至150張病床。<br />\n<br />\n路透社／英國《衞報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uax8AbDPUJrGbkpEYY0o0h99q3M=/190x115/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K7K2GOXDIXESMMBBRPW54DCAKI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fuax8AbDPUJrGbkpEYY0o0h99q3M%3D%2F190x115%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK7K2GOXDIXESMMBBRPW54DCAKI.jpg&h=0ce5d1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反政府示威者上街抗議，遭軍人阻止。"},{"pid":"2adac27ac5e7180168e14dcb1ebd8d7cf307f770","tid":2145594,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:34:16.000Z","msg":"祖國既戰狼呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6c39aa0312acb554d38d77baeec831ec4d8bb8","tid":2145594,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"黎巴嫰真係好撚渣<br />\n學禾地大支那咁話只死35人再拉哂所有造謠人士咪得囉"},{"pid":"0ac097d903b5ff32e58947ab6730a65cbd9d3fc5","tid":2145594,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c6c39aa0312acb554d38d77baeec831ec4d8bb8","tid":2145594,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"黎巴嫰真係好撚渣<br />\n學禾地大支那咁話只死35人再拉哂所有造謠人士咪得囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:38:39.000Z","msg":"好垃圾<br />\n仲學人成立委員會調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果林鄭搞搵求其搵個監港口會出個真相報告就冇事了"},{"pid":"d679ab942d9bc1597b087bb305939c69369b9f91","tid":2145594,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ac097d903b5ff32e58947ab6730a65cbd9d3fc5","tid":2145594,"uid":3860,"like":